WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.520
Endi Androidda. ListView dan tashqari qayta ko‘rib chiqa 

00:00:02.520 --> 00:00:05.850
oladigan view larning har xil turlari mavjud.

00:00:05.850 --> 00:00:09.105
Ular GridView yoki RecyclerView bo‘lishi mumkin.

00:00:09.105 --> 00:00:10.845
lekin keyingi slaydlarda,

00:00:10.845 --> 00:00:15.495
men sizga dasturchi view larni qachon 
qayta ishlatishi kerakligi va view lar 

00:00:15.495 --> 00:00:18.810
soni baribir oz bo‘lgani uchun qachon qayta ishlatish 

00:00:18.810 --> 00:00:22.770
haqida qayg‘urmasligini, ayrim bir 
holatlarni ko‘rsatib o‘tmoqchiman.

00:00:22.770 --> 00:00:25.710
Twitter ilovasida, juda ham ko‘p tvitlar bor.

00:00:25.710 --> 00:00:30.075
Siz ularni pastga qarab aylantirishingiz mumkin, 
lekin uning uchun soatlar ketishi turgan gap. 

00:00:30.075 --> 00:00:32.400
Ammo biz aqlli qaror qilib, talabda bo‘lgan

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:35.430
viewlarni foydalanuvchi aylantirgan 
paytida ko‘rsatsak bo‘ladi,

00:00:35.430 --> 00:00:37.898
bu degani biz view larni qayta ishlatishimiz mumkin.

00:00:37.898 --> 00:00:41.745
Google Fit ilovasi foydalanuvchilarga 
ularning kundalik fitnesi haqida ma’lumot beradi.

00:00:41.745 --> 00:00:46.620
Foydalanuvchi qilgan harakati, masalan, tushda yugurgan vaqtini, kuzatib borishi mumkin. 

00:00:46.620 --> 00:00:50.367
Va ilova faol vaqt, umumiy vaqt,
taxminiy masofa, qadamlar va ma’lum 

00:00:50.367 --> 00:00:53.235
bir faoliyatga sarflangan kaloriyalar 

00:00:53.235 --> 00:00:57.450
ro‘yxati sahifasini taqdim etadi.

00:00:57.450 --> 00:01:00.780
Xo‘sh, ilova ko‘rsatadigan ma’lum bir o‘lchovlar soni bo‘lgani sababli,

00:01:00.780 --> 00:01:02.625
view larni yangilashga hojat yo‘q.

00:01:02.625 --> 00:01:05.715
Bu ilova qismi vertikal 
LinearLayoutni ishlata oladi.

00:01:05.715 --> 00:01:07.785
Moliyaga qiziqishi bo‘lganlar diqqatiga,

00:01:07.785 --> 00:01:11.460
"Stocks real time stock" ilovasi, 
foydalanuvchilarga o‘zlari qiziqtirgan aksiyalarni 

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:15.765
kuzatib borish va ularni portfoliolariga qo‘shish imkoniyatini beradi.

00:01:15.765 --> 00:01:19.920
Va foydalanuvchilar o‘zlarini qiziqtirgan 
ko‘plab kompaniyalarga ega bo‘lishi odatiy holdir, 

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.810
shuning uchun ro‘yxat ancha uzun bo‘lishi mumkin.

00:01:21.810 --> 00:01:24.930
Ilova samarali ravishda mana bu kompaniyalar haqidagi 
hamma ma’lumotni har safar foydalanuvchi pastga 

00:01:24.930 --> 00:01:29.820
aylantira boshlaganida view larni qayta 
yangilab namoyish qilishi mumkin.

00:01:29.820 --> 00:01:31.725
Bu mashqqa keladigan bo‘lsak,

00:01:31.725 --> 00:01:34.440
men sizlardan vaqt sarflab, qurilmangizdagi ilovadan 
yoki mashhur Android ilovalaridan ikkita 

00:01:34.440 --> 00:01:38.970
misol keltirishingizni xohlardim.

00:01:38.970 --> 00:01:42.120
Birinchi misolda, vertikal Linear Layoutni
 hamma elementlar ro‘yxati uchun ishlatish 

00:01:42.120 --> 00:01:45.465
yaxshi g‘oya hisoblanadi.

00:01:45.465 --> 00:01:47.120
Ikkinchi misolga kelsak,

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:51.300
biz shunday ilova topishimiz kerakki, u views larni ListViewga
 o‘xshash narsa bilan qayta ishlatishi kerak bo‘ladi.

00:01:51.300 --> 00:01:53.370
So‘ng siz javoblaringiz bilan muhokama forumida ulashishingizni xohlardim, 

00:01:53.370 --> 00:01:57.080
boshqa o‘quvchilar bilan fikr almashish maqsadida. 

